WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:09.280
Do you want to be a TV news reporter? People often ask me why I love my job. Well, it's

00:09.280 --> 00:15.760
very exciting. I'm the first to know about important news stories. I travel around the

00:15.760 --> 00:23.400
world and I talk to important and famous people. But you have to learn a lot of things if

00:23.400 --> 00:31.560
you want to work in TV news, such as how to use a video camera, how to write news reports,

00:31.560 --> 00:38.920
and how to speak to the camera. A good place to learn to be a TV news reporter is a small

00:38.920 --> 00:46.120
television station. You get a lot of practice doing different things so you can learn fast.

